      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "The Crimson Glow",
        "Client": "Guild Master Hojo",
        "Description": "Ancient texts speak of the\r\nCrimson Glow Valstrax as the\r\n\u0022Scourge of the World.\u0022 Well,\r\nnow that it\u0027s returned, we won\u0027t\r\nlet it destroy the peace that\r\nKamura has fought so hard for!\r\nTime to hop to it-to it!",
        "Target": "Slay a Crimson Glow Valstrax",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "La lueur \u00E9carlate",
        "Client": "Hojo le Ma\u00EEtre de la Guilde",
        "Description": "Les textes anciens parlent du\r\nValstrax \u00E9carlate comme\r\nd\u0027un fl\u00E9au sans pareil.\r\nLe voil\u00E0 de retour... Pas\r\nquestion de le laisser ruiner\r\nla paix pour laquelle\r\nle village s\u0027est tant battu !",
